title: Watch: Kylie Jenner gets $320k Rolls Royce Ghost for her 18th. Also has Instagram doppleganger
text:
Kylie Jenner sees your 2003 Nissan Micra runaround you'd be damn lucky to get for your 18th, and raises you this fine motor in all its cream leather loveliness.
And then, just to rub it in / state the bleedin' obvious a little bit more...
WOW. What 18-year-old needs this kind of car? @KylieJenner DRIVES OFF IN A BRAND NEW $320,000 ROLLS ROYCE GHOST pic.twitter.com/anM4BwCAVe
â€” Famaglam (@Fama_glam) October 5, 2015
We tend to agree... Well, at least there's no way she'd ever be tempted to drink drive given she's under 21? (Never EVER drink and drive, people).
In other news, the internet has located Kylie's doppelganger - and it's not big sister Kim.
The gas thing is, Gaby Waters looks more like Kylie Jenner than Kylie Jenner does - if you know what I mean?
Via Us Weekly
